                      </svg></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="founder-member-scheme_testimonial_slide-nav w-slider-nav w-slider-nav-invert w-round"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="section_founder-member-scheme_faq">
        <div class="padding-global">
          <div class="container-large">
            <div class="padding-section-large">
              <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_component">
                <div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge">
                  <div class="text-align-center">
                    <div class="max-width-large align-center">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small">
                        <h2 class="heading-style-h2-6">FAQs</h2>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-size-medium-2">Find answers to common questions about our founder member scheme</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="max-width-large align-center">
                  <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_list">
                    <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_item">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <div class="text-size-medium-2 text-weight-bold">How does the scheme work?</div>
                      </div>
                      <p>The scheme invites 100 donors to contribute £100 or more within 100 days. Each donor receives special recognition and an invitation to our launch party.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_item">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <div class="text-size-medium-2 text-weight-bold">What are the benefits?</div>
                      </div>
                      <p>Benefits include exclusive launch party invitation, recognition in our materials, and direct impact on our mission.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_item">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <div class="text-size-medium-2 text-weight-bold">Can I donate more?</div>
                      </div>
                      <p>Absolutely. We welcome donations above the £100 minimum. Larger contributions provide greater support to our initiatives.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_item">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <div class="text-size-medium-2 text-weight-bold">Is my donation tax-deductible?</div>
                      </div>
                      <p>We recommend consulting your tax advisor. Many donations to charitable initiatives qualify for tax deductions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="founder-member-scheme_faq_item">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <div class="text-size-medium-2 text-weight-bold">How will my donation be used?</div>
                      </div>
                      <p>Every pound directly supports our core mission of creating sustainable social impact across communities.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="margin-top margin-xxlarge">
                  <div class="text-align-center">
                    <div class="max-width-medium align-center">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-xsmall">
                        <h3 class="heading-style-h4">Need more information?</h3>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-size-medium-2">Our team is ready to answer any additional questions</p>
                      <div class="margin-top margin-medium">
                        <div class="button-group is-center faq">
                          <div class="contact15_item">
                            <div class="contact15_item-icon-wrapper">
